              <div class="card-meta">
                <span class="owasp-tag">OWASP A03:2021</span>
                <span class="risk-badge risk-critical">CRITICAL</span>
                <span class="owasp-tag">CWE-94</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-description">
              JavaScript code is executed via <code>eval()</code>. Python code is run via
              <code>child_process.exec('python3 -c ...')</code>. Both allow full system access.
            </p>
            <button class="expand-toggle" data-target="rce-details">
              <span class="arrow">▶</span> Payloads
            </button>
            <div class="expand-content" id="rce-details">
              <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:4px">JavaScript (eval):</p>
              <ul class="payload-list">
                <li class="payload-item">
                  <span class="payload-code" data-target="js-code">require('os').hostname()</span>
                  <button class="copy-btn">📋</button>
                </li>
                <li class="payload-item">
                  <span class="payload-code" data-target="js-code">require('fs').readdirSync('.')</span>
                  <button class="copy-btn">📋</button>
                </li>
                <li class="payload-item">
                  <span class="payload-code" data-target="js-code">process.env</span>
                  <button class="copy-btn">📋</button>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin:8px 0 4px">Python (exec):</p>
              <ul class="payload-list">
                <li class="payload-item">
                  <span class="payload-code" data-target="python-code">import os; print(os.getcwd())</span>
                  <button class="copy-btn">📋</button>
                </li>
                <li class="payload-item">
                  <span class="payload-code" data-target="python-code">import socket; print(socket.gethostname())</span>
                  <button class="copy-btn">📋</button>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <div class="mitigation-panel">
                <div class="mitigation-title">✅ Mitigations</div>
                <ul class="mitigation-list">
                  <li>Never use eval() with user input</li>
                  <li>Use sandboxed VMs (vm2) for isolated execution</li>
                  <li>Avoid shell execution with user data</li>
                  <li>Use parameterized commands, not string concat</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-try">
            <div class="try-label">🧪 Try It — JavaScript eval()</div>
