          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-description">
              Session cookies lack <code>HttpOnly</code> and <code>Secure</code> flags, making them
              readable via <code>document.cookie</code>. Session values can be overwritten by
              POST request to impersonate any user.
            </p>
            <div style="background:rgba(79,142,247,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(79,142,247,0.2);border-radius:8px;padding:10px 14px;font-size:12px;margin-top:8px">
