                  <li>Set HttpOnly flag on session cookies</li>
                  <li>Set Secure flag (HTTPS only)</li>
                  <li>Set SameSite=Strict or Lax</li>
                  <li>Regenerate session ID after login</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
