              <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Expiry</span><span class="info-value">None (token never expires)</span></div>
              <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Role trust</span><span class="info-value">Server trusts role from payload</span></div>
              <div class="mitigation-panel">
                <div class="mitigation-title">✅ Mitigations</div>
                <ul class="mitigation-list">
                  <li>Use strong, random 256-bit secrets</li>
                  <li>Always set expiresIn (short TTL)</li>
                  <li>Store JWTs in HttpOnly cookies, not localStorage</li>
                  <li>Validate claims server-side, don't trust blindly</li>
